{"tid":404481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(絲打入) 有甲狀腺既你入！！！","createTime":"2017-09-18T06:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T18:17:37.000Z","uid":146740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7601b1174f7fcaf73c6ed85006656784e1dce017","tid":404481,"uid":146740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:40:43.000Z","msg":"我兩年前睇急症明明唔關甲狀腺事，<br />\n跟住就無啦啦話我係甲狀腺出現問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身都好瘦，自從食左佢粒綠色藥之後就係短時間內暴肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由45kg去到而家58kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家仲食緊佢隻綠色藥，問左醫生話唔關事，但上網睇左好多人都同我差唔多情況，都係因為咁肥左好多<br />\n我有做運動，正常飲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想問下有無絲打係有甲狀腺而成功瘦番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？？"},{"pid":"20f27e218a580a15c912b89802296f29c5c4feea","tid":404481,"uid":68236,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:46:44.000Z","msg":"甲狀腺係人都有架啦<br />\n你以前瘦係因為甲亢<br />\n食藥降返正常所以咪無咁瘦<br />\n但健康重要啲嘛"},{"pid":"256b7983135d82faa1a3b717686f3fd3a710e7c4","tid":404481,"uid":48796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:46:44.000Z","msg":"人人都有甲狀腺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喺條頸, 分泌甲狀腺素<br />\n<br />\n初初咩病癥睇急症? 醫生診斷後話咩病? 粒藥乜嘢名? 覆診有冇同醫生講你問題? 全部唔講點討論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294583eefacd71016e5abf95bcd13dc61b0f6adc","tid":404481,"uid":68236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:48:09.000Z","msg":"甲狀腺係人都有架啦<br />\n你以前瘦係因為甲亢<br />\n食藥降返正常所以咪無咁瘦<br />\n但健康重要啲嘛"},{"pid":"36a94374801d65d898b122edfb65eb43b581bc2b","tid":404481,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:48:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>甲狀腺係人都有架啦<br />\n你以前瘦係因為甲亢<br />\n食藥降返正常所以咪無咁瘦<br />\n但健康重要啲嘛</blockquote><br />\n佢隻眼係咪會眼突?"},{"pid":"06229153e33c5e6cc93f73b76db63c95596713b6","tid":404481,"uid":146740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:56:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>甲狀腺係人都有架啦<br />\n你以前瘦係因為甲亢<br />\n食藥降返正常所以咪無咁瘦<br />\n但健康重要啲嘛</blockquote><br />\n佢隻眼係咪會眼突?</blockquote><br />\n我症狀係，有小小眼突<br />\n心跳會快，手會小小震<br />\n甲狀腺無腫<br />\n體重上我一路都係45-50kg，係自從話我有病之後體重先出現變化"},{"pid":"fb715c44cfef9528587359f12060c1f20c91e38b","tid":404481,"uid":146740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:59:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人人都有甲狀腺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喺條頸, 分泌甲狀腺素<br />\n<br />\n初初咩病癥睇急症? 醫生診斷後話咩病? 粒藥乜嘢名? 覆診有冇同醫生講你問題? 全部唔講點討論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n初初因為感冒唔食藥搞到攻到隻眼到，隻眼紅曬，睇嘢好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去睇急症話我隻眼無事，但就因為我心跳快就打尖睇左我先，跟住就無啦啦話唔記得左佢話甲亢定甲減<br />\n不過我諗我係甲亢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc9481b6219c2e0932ae34162e33e6a8ba3120e","tid":404481,"uid":83173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:39:26.000Z","msg":"我甲亢 食綠色藥冇肥過 食左幾年"},{"pid":"cd2831f629ec91a4125b5a0c9617c00f96cf84ce","tid":404481,"uid":146740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:56:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我甲亢 食綠色藥冇肥過 食左幾年</blockquote><br />\n醫生好似有講過係因為新陳代謝慢所以好難瘦番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都唔知同綠色藥有無關係，但我上網睇過好多人有食都肥左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35da6c77a580e80fc791a873a518c25273effc01","tid":404481,"uid":83173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:33:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我甲亢 食綠色藥冇肥過 食左幾年</blockquote><br />\n醫生好似有講過係因為新陳代謝慢所以好難瘦番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都唔知同綠色藥有無關係，但我上網睇過好多人有食都肥左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我冇肥過keep 某個體重， 食呢隻藥唔代表會減慢新陳代謝。只係我地甲亢高，新陳代謝比正常人快。我食左幾年個體重都冇加都咁喎，你平時飲食習慣如何呢？"},{"pid":"79c807fd519f128a0712ee4c9f414277f3ac2436","tid":404481,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:46:09.000Z","msg":"新陳代謝快唔係會瘦咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd661233064f4cecda8bf66031b7fdd95b507f8","tid":404481,"uid":83173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:40:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新陳代謝快唔係會瘦咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以我都想知樓主最近甲狀腺指數如何，加上食降甲狀腺素唔會肥"},{"pid":"e52ad88f162f463c708299b5dde791a351c8bc2a","tid":404481,"uid":146740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新陳代謝快唔係會瘦咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係慢"},{"pid":"41ea06df21482182230e80c5f36b16c2818307ee","tid":404481,"uid":146740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:02:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>新陳代謝快唔係會瘦咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以我都想知樓主最近甲狀腺指數如何，加上食降甲狀腺素唔會肥</blockquote><br />\n我而家就食緊一日一粒藥，指數就正常，但體重仍然無上無落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e0e91815938f009c322b42fb5ea617149f55ca","tid":404481,"uid":146740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:23:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我甲亢 食綠色藥冇肥過 食左幾年</blockquote><br />\n醫生好似有講過係因為新陳代謝慢所以好難瘦番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都唔知同綠色藥有無關係，但我上網睇過好多人有食都肥左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我冇肥過keep 某個體重， 食呢隻藥唔代表會減慢新陳代謝。只係我地甲亢高，新陳代謝比正常人快。我食左幾年個體重都冇加都咁喎，你平時飲食習慣如何呢？</blockquote><br />\n飲食正常，無暴飲暴食，食菜多，一星期都有做幾日運動<br />\n仲健康過以前，以前日日食麥當勞飲可樂都唔會肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286f285cd3ed7b7566c102644ca61aaf62cb146c","tid":404481,"uid":59953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:37:03.000Z","msg":"我停左藥2年左右而家又復發"},{"pid":"faffea97381301c399f2c5df41fcd961c999cd72","tid":404481,"uid":146740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:47:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我停左藥2年左右而家又復發</blockquote><br />\n我食藥食左一年左右停左藥，半年之後又復發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢問我飲唔飲碘水，但飲左一係就好番，一係就食成世藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447b43ee0b75387231c2f5fcc2454db5e2b5577f","tid":404481,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:52:05.000Z","msg":"係肥咗啫, 再做多啲運動囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821b669c542b7280d43ea80d5bfee6933eb90b06","tid":404481,"uid":146740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:55:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係肥咗啫, 再做多啲運動囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係咁簡單就解決到就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf8e734cd3d83a77e3fa467a0318c9fbc0a558f","tid":404481,"uid":59953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:17:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係肥咗啫, 再做多啲運動囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係咁簡單就解決到就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點都好過唔食藥<br />\n會成身冇力"},{"pid":"8d09d1314c84c3f26c8db63d4131dcfb44eea21f","tid":404481,"uid":146740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T18:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係肥咗啫, 再做多啲運動囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係咁簡單就解決到就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點都好過唔食藥<br />\n會成身冇力</blockquote><br />\n咁緊係唔會唔食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係唔係咁肥姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c15a7af6fb6a0101fe79cab23872aa4767a77403","tid":404481,"uid":146740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T18:17:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係肥咗啫, 再做多啲運動囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係咁簡單就解決到就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點都好過唔食藥<br />\n會成身冇力</blockquote><br />\n咁緊係唔會唔食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係唔係咁肥姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n*唔想"}]}